public class Make
extends AntBuild
implements Tasks

Packages the mkr distribution. The build targets are:

compile
Compiles the java files in build
jar
Builds mkr jar file
docs
Creates javadocs
dist
Creates a distribution
tidy
Deletes binaries
clean
Deletes binaries and javadocs
